46724fdb-70d8-4b00-9550-b7ac60959046.title: Lorelai
46724fdb-70d8-4b00-9550-b7ac60959046.text:
Hello! I'm Lorelai. Welcome to the Warriors' Guild
basement!

72bbb3de-3168-41c7-86d6-58e4ed9cce26.title: <player>
72bbb3de-3168-41c7-86d6-58e4ed9cce26.text: What are you doing down here?

4183926f-eee2-4d80-ac91-61dc52f47be9.title: Lorelai
4183926f-eee2-4d80-ac91-61dc52f47be9.text:
I'm training this group of special Cyclopes to be
stronger and more powerful for Kamfreena.

options.text: How exactly are you training them?

0a8dfa08-80db-43a0-b2d2-108be420192f.title: Lorelai
0a8dfa08-80db-43a0-b2d2-108be420192f.text:
They have a chance of dropping a new, more powerful
defender. Kamfreena doesn't want just anyone getting
their hands on one so she moved them down here and
tasked me with training them.

bf7decbf-8654-495a-8f71-e1828e6bad44.title: <player>
bf7decbf-8654-495a-8f71-e1828e6bad44.text: How exactly are you training them?

98d985d8-bb87-4eac-b9aa-3012c02baf5a.title: Lorelai
98d985d8-bb87-4eac-b9aa-3012c02baf5a.text:
With a punishing routine of combat, fighting and the
odd death!

a82502c4-2e20-4686-babb-00789e24d6d8.title: <player>
a82502c4-2e20-4686-babb-00789e24d6d8.text:
So, you just let them fight each other and hope they get
stronger?

522648be-ec9f-4d5f-b6f0-8455d9057c10.title: Lorelai
522648be-ec9f-4d5f-b6f0-8455d9057c10.text:
Of course not, that would just be cruel! Kamfreena and
I only allow the most worthy of adventurers to fight
these cyclopes.

1726fe3b-4b06-4dc1-9391-9db6bb0a14d3.title: <player>
1726fe3b-4b06-4dc1-9391-9db6bb0a14d3.text: I am a mighty adventurer! Can I fight them?

c492e9ca-c3a7-44f7-a387-e3db7a7673b1.title: Lorelai
c492e9ca-c3a7-44f7-a387-e3db7a7673b1.text:
You'll need to display your skills as a Warrior before I
can allow you to enter the room.

ce2dcff2-9518-4070-8d6a-bbfe1b30fc3f.title: Lorelai
ce2dcff2-9518-4070-8d6a-bbfe1b30fc3f.text:
Bring me a Rune Defender and I shall unlock the
door for you, this shows me you have dedicated enough
time to fighting the Cyclops upstairs.

options.text: I have a Rune Defender here.

6478d22e-246d-4af9-9cdd-e2b44f2b2a55.title: <player>
6478d22e-246d-4af9-9cdd-e2b44f2b2a55.text: I have a Rune Defender here, please let me in!

15cf2cb2-9cf2-4488-ae09-a9eff5a9ecd0.title: Lorelai
15cf2cb2-9cf2-4488-ae09-a9eff5a9ecd0.text: Very well, I have unlocked the door for you.

3eb1e2ec-6579-442d-a324-33aa4cdd827b.title: Lorelai
3eb1e2ec-6579-442d-a324-33aa4cdd827b.text:
And the Wise Old Man is my Dad... come back when
you have the Rune Defender!
